<H3> <TI>   Bank Profiled on Eve of Privatization </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Bank Profiled on Eve of Privatization </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   WS2305115894 Warsaw NOWA EUROPA in Polish 23 May 94 p 17 </F>
<F P=103> WS2305115894 </F>
<F P=104>  Warsaw NOWA EUROPA </F>
