<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] [Words indistinct] [Prime Minister] Haris Silajdzic 
today despite [words indistinct] also received a delegation of 
the Islamic Republic of Iran led by (Ibrahim Rahimpur), director 
general for Central and Northern Europe at the Iranian Foreign 
Ministry. The talks were also attended by Iranian Ambassador to 
Bosnia-Herzegovina Muhammad Asayesh-Zarebi. 
  During the frank and friendly talks, (Rahimpur) conveyed the 
impressions of Minister Velayati to Prime Minister Silajdzic and 
