  [Bratislava PRAVDA in Slovak on 20 May on page 3 carries a 
200-word "vy"-signed report on the above poll, which adds the 
following information: 
"Democratic Union supporters had the most confidence in Jozef 
Moravcik -- 75 percent, 
Movement for a Democratic Slovakia supporters in Vladimir Meciar 
-- 69 percent, 
Party of the Democratic Left supporters in Peter Weiss -- 59 
percent, and 
Christian Democratic Movement supporters in Jan Carnogursky -- 
51 percent. 
A total of 66 politicians were named by the respondents."] 

