<H3> <TI>   One Killed, Nine Wounded in Grenade Explosion </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    One Killed, Nine Wounded in Grenade Explosion </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   LD2705100194 Belgrade TANJUG in English 0944 GMT 27 May 94 </F>
<F P=103> LD2705100194 </F>
<F P=104>  Belgrade TANJUG </F>
<F P=105>  English </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] Vrnjacka Banja, May 27 (TANJUG) -- One person was 
killed and nine wounded when a hand granade exploded in a bus 
full of passengers travelling from Krusevac to Vrnjacka Banja in 
the central part of the Yugoslav Republic of Serbia on Thursday 
night [26 May]. The person suspected of having thrown the 
granade into the bus was arrested after the incident. 
Investigation is under way. 

